> Service


> Repository



### Database used in project

* MySql

### Project Summary

This is a __Doctor-App__ built with Java Spring Boot, using MySql database engine and Maven build tool. The system supports booking appointments by patients for a particular doctor. The project follows the Model-View-Controller (MVC) architecture pattern, with separate layers for controller, service, and repository.